						               													<description>Lemonade for sale! Work as a team to make and serve enough cups of lemonade to fill your money jar. Shake up the dice and roll for the match! Get the ingredients needed to serve a customer and add a few quarters to the money jar. Miss the match and it&amp;rsquo;s a sour lemon for the team. Cooperate to win! No reading required. INCLUDES: 5 dice, 1 plastic cup, 12 customer cards, 4 sour lemon tokens, 12 quarter tokens, 1 recipe card, 1 money card, and instructions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In this quick cooperative game, players take turns rolling dice (up to three times) in an effort to complete recipes for lemonade, strawberry lemonade or limeade. There are a variety of customers and each has a specific order and quarters in hand. The more difficult the drink recipe, the bigger the payout! Win by filling your jar with 12 quarters. But, fail to roll the correct ingredients too many times, and the sour lemons will cause your team to lose.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
